{"word":"G4881 - συναπόλλυμι - synapóllymi - soon-ap-ol'-loo-mee - Perish with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναπόλλυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synapóllymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ap-ol'-loo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Perish with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடச்சேதமாகு"},{"paragraph":"to destroy together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G622 - ἀπόλλυμι - apóllymi - ap-ol'-loo-mee/622\">G622</a>; to <i>destroy</i> (middle voice or passive voice, <i>be slain</i>) in company <i>with:</i> - perish with.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}